00:25:58,980 --> 00:26:00,099
[SPEAKER_00] Oraheli,

801
00:26:00,099 --> 00:26:01,859
[SPEAKER_00] sada dolazimo do važnosti

802
00:26:01,859 --> 00:26:02,539
[SPEAKER_00] sa Benjaminom,

803
00:26:02,539 --> 00:26:05,400
[SPEAKER_00] Oraheli i njezinom rađenju Benjamina.

804
00:26:05,940 --> 00:26:07,460
[SPEAKER_00] Dakle, one se nalaze na putu

805
00:26:07,460 --> 00:26:08,680
[SPEAKER_00] Kamo u Betlehem.

806
00:26:08,680 --> 00:26:09,700
[SPEAKER_00] Sigurno ste šokirani,

807
00:26:09,700 --> 00:26:10,180
[SPEAKER_00] je li tako?

808
00:26:10,180 --> 00:26:12,619
[SPEAKER_00] Potom odu iz Betela.

809
00:26:12,619 --> 00:26:15,000
[SPEAKER_00] Još bijaše malo puta do Efrate,

810
00:26:15,000 --> 00:26:16,960
[SPEAKER_00] a Rahela se nađe pri porođaju.

811
00:26:16,960 --> 00:26:18,740
[SPEAKER_00] Napali je teški trudovi.

812
00:26:18,740 --> 00:26:21,079
[SPEAKER_00] Kad su je porođajni bolovi bili najteži,

813
00:26:21,079 --> 00:26:22,079
[SPEAKER_00] rečeo je babica.

814
00:26:22,079 --> 00:26:23,180
[SPEAKER_00] Ne boj se,

815
00:26:23,180 --> 00:26:24,640
[SPEAKER_00] jer ti je i ovo sin.

816
00:26:24,640 --> 00:26:26,579
[SPEAKER_00] Kad se rastavljala s dušom,

817
00:26:26,579 --> 00:26:27,859
[SPEAKER_00] jer umiraše Rahela,

818
00:26:27,859 --> 00:26:30,380
[SPEAKER_00] nađenu sinu ime Ben-Oni,

819
00:26:30,380 --> 00:26:32,480
[SPEAKER_00] ali ga otac prozva Benjamin.

820
00:26:32,480 --> 00:26:34,799
[SPEAKER_00] Objasniću značenje imena.

821
00:26:35,299 --> 00:26:36,359
[SPEAKER_00] Tako umrije Rahela.

822
00:26:36,359 --> 00:26:38,359
[SPEAKER_00] Sahran je na putu u Efratu,

823
00:26:38,359 --> 00:26:39,759
[SPEAKER_00] to jest Betlehem.

824
00:26:39,759 --> 00:26:41,200
[SPEAKER_00] A na njezinu grobu

825
00:26:41,200 --> 00:26:42,640
[SPEAKER_00] Jakov podigne spomenik.

826
00:26:42,640 --> 00:26:44,299
[SPEAKER_00] One što je na Rahelinu grobu

827
00:26:44,299 --> 00:26:45,160
[SPEAKER_00] do danas.

828
00:26:45,160 --> 00:26:46,299
[SPEAKER_00] Dakle, pozdne,

829
00:26:46,299 --> 00:26:47,519
[SPEAKER_00] zna se gdje je njezin grob

830
00:26:47,519 --> 00:26:49,440
[SPEAKER_00] i tamo i da danas odlaze židovi

831
00:26:49,440 --> 00:26:52,519
[SPEAKER_00] i ona je kao jedna velika zagovarateljica

832
00:26:52,519 --> 00:26:54,400
[SPEAKER_00] i simbol židovske majke

833
00:26:54,400 --> 00:26:55,079
[SPEAKER_00] koja pati,

834
00:26:55,079 --> 00:26:55,859
[SPEAKER_00] koja trpi.

835
00:26:56,740 --> 00:26:58,279
[SPEAKER_00] Dakle, sjetite se Mihej,

836
00:26:58,279 --> 00:27:00,000
[SPEAKER_00] prorok Mihej 5. Jan kaže,

837
00:27:00,000 --> 00:27:01,519
[SPEAKER_00] a ti Betleheme Efrato.

838
00:27:01,519 --> 00:27:02,519
[SPEAKER_00] Zašto kaže Efrato?

839
00:27:02,519 --> 00:27:04,400
[SPEAKER_00] Jer želju odvući na ovu situaciju

840
00:27:04,400 --> 00:27:05,960
[SPEAKER_00] sa Rahelom i njezinim porođajem.

841
00:27:05,960 --> 00:27:08,279
[SPEAKER_00] Dakle, ona je, dok je rađala Benjamina,

842
00:27:08,279 --> 00:27:08,819
[SPEAKER_00] umrla.

843
00:27:08,819 --> 00:27:09,680
[SPEAKER_00] O tako?

844
00:27:09,680 --> 00:27:11,960
[SPEAKER_00] Najmanji među knježevstvima judinim,

845
00:27:11,960 --> 00:27:14,640
[SPEAKER_00] iste mi će mi izaći onaj koji će vladati Izraelom.

846
00:27:14,640 --> 00:27:16,000
[SPEAKER_00] Njegov je iskon od Davida,

847
00:27:16,000 --> 00:27:17,500
[SPEAKER_00] od dječnih vremena.

848
00:27:17,500 --> 00:27:18,700
[SPEAKER_00] E sada,

849
00:27:18,700 --> 00:27:22,000
[SPEAKER_00] doći ćemo upravo za koji trenutak,

850
00:27:22,000 --> 00:27:25,200
[SPEAKER_00] analizirat ćemo pokolj nevjene dječice.

851
00:27:25,200 --> 00:27:27,279
[SPEAKER_00] Možda zato nije dobro da su djeca ovdje,

852
00:27:27,279 --> 00:27:28,640
[SPEAKER_00] ovo je više za 18+.

853
00:27:28,640 --> 00:27:32,259
[SPEAKER_00] Dakle, vrlo je važno

854
00:27:32,259 --> 00:27:33,220
[SPEAKER_00] da to analiziramo.

855
00:27:33,220 --> 00:27:37,359
[SPEAKER_00] Imaćemo jedan onako malo drugačiji pristup

856
00:27:37,359 --> 00:27:39,680
[SPEAKER_00] koja je zapravo bila, ajmo reći,

857
00:27:39,680 --> 00:27:41,599
[SPEAKER_00] uloga svete obitelji

858
00:27:41,599 --> 00:27:43,220
[SPEAKER_00] u pokolju nevjene dječice

859
00:27:43,220 --> 00:27:45,519
[SPEAKER_00] u smislu nisu samo bježali,

860
00:27:45,519 --> 00:27:47,240
[SPEAKER_00] nego još jedna uloga.

861
00:27:47,240 --> 00:27:48,880
[SPEAKER_00] Nešto vrlo, vrlo važno.

862
00:27:48,880 --> 00:27:51,619
[SPEAKER_00] Dakle, zato i Matej

863
00:27:51,619 --> 00:27:53,500
[SPEAKER_00] kada opisuje pokolj nevjene dječice,

864
00:27:53,500 --> 00:27:55,759
[SPEAKER_00] sjetite se, dakle,

865
00:27:55,759 --> 00:27:57,960
[SPEAKER_00] on citira proroka Jeremiju.

866
00:27:57,960 --> 00:28:00,799
[SPEAKER_00] I u tom citatu proroka Jeremije,

867
00:28:00,799 --> 00:28:02,640
[SPEAKER_00] a to Jeremija je govorio tada

868
00:28:02,640 --> 00:28:07,079
[SPEAKER_00] kada su popilonci zauzeli Jeruzalem,

869
00:28:07,079 --> 00:28:08,880
[SPEAKER_00] kada su istirali Izraelce,

870
00:28:08,880 --> 00:28:10,680
[SPEAKER_00] kada su počeli ubijati Izraelce,

871
00:28:10,680 --> 00:28:12,279
[SPEAKER_00] dakle, i kaže se

872
00:28:12,279 --> 00:28:14,500
[SPEAKER_00] čuj, u rabi se, kukanje čuje

873
00:28:14,500 --> 00:28:15,519
[SPEAKER_00] i gorak plać.

874
00:28:15,519 --> 00:28:18,059
[SPEAKER_00] Rahela oplakuje sinove svoje,

875
00:28:18,059 --> 00:28:18,640
[SPEAKER_00] dakle, vidite,

876
00:28:18,640 --> 00:28:21,079
[SPEAKER_00] tu jednu snažu židovsku tradiciju,

877
00:28:21,079 --> 00:28:23,480
[SPEAKER_00] smatrite Rahelu i dalje živom.

878
00:28:23,480 --> 00:28:24,759
[SPEAKER_00] Iako ona već stoljećima

879
00:28:24,759 --> 00:28:27,759
[SPEAKER_00] mrtva prije nego što se dogodilo,

880
00:28:27,759 --> 00:28:28,619
[SPEAKER_00] ovo zbabiloncima,

881
00:28:28,619 --> 00:28:30,119
[SPEAKER_00] ali oni je smatraju velikom,

882
00:28:30,119 --> 00:28:32,220
[SPEAKER_00] dakle, ona pati sa svojim narodom.

883
00:28:32,220 --> 00:28:34,720
[SPEAKER_00] Tako, Rahela pati sa svojim narodom.

884
00:28:34,720 --> 00:28:36,160
[SPEAKER_00] Kroz stoljeća, jel' tako?

885
00:28:36,160 --> 00:28:38,240
[SPEAKER_00] Rahela oplakuje sinove svoje

886
00:28:38,240 --> 00:28:40,079
[SPEAKER_00] i neće da se utješi za djecom,

887
00:28:40,079 --> 00:28:41,180
[SPEAKER_00] jer njih više nema.

888
00:28:41,180 --> 00:28:42,359
[SPEAKER_00] To Mate koristi,

889
00:28:42,359 --> 00:28:43,259
[SPEAKER_00] sjećate se,

890
00:28:43,259 --> 00:28:44,359
[SPEAKER_00] kada opisuje,

891
00:28:44,359 --> 00:28:45,400
[SPEAKER_00] kada daje izvještaj

892
00:28:45,400 --> 00:28:47,119
[SPEAKER_00] o pokolju nevjede dječice.

893
00:28:47,119 --> 00:28:48,700
[SPEAKER_00] Međutim,

894
00:28:48,700 --> 00:28:50,099
[SPEAKER_00] prije nego što sad kredemo

895
00:28:50,099 --> 00:28:51,359
[SPEAKER_00] na pokolju nevjede dječice,

896
00:28:51,579 --> 00:28:52,400
[SPEAKER_00] idemo vidjeti, dakle,

897
00:28:52,400 --> 00:28:54,680
[SPEAKER_00] tu situaciju sa Benjaminom.

898
00:28:54,680 --> 00:28:56,920
[SPEAKER_00] Da vidite zapravo da u starom zavijetu

899
00:28:56,920 --> 00:28:59,420
[SPEAKER_00] roditelji Izrela su Jakovi i Rahela,

900
00:28:59,420 --> 00:29:02,039
[SPEAKER_00] u novom zavijetu roditelji crkve

901
00:29:02,039 --> 00:29:03,900
[SPEAKER_00] su Marija i Josip.

902
00:29:03,900 --> 00:29:08,900
[SPEAKER_00] Ovako, ona je nazvala sina Ben-oni.

903
00:29:08,900 --> 00:29:10,940
[SPEAKER_00] Sjetite se, Rahela kad ga je rodila.

904
00:29:10,940 --> 00:29:13,420
[SPEAKER_00] Ben-oni znači sin moje boli.

905
00:29:13,420 --> 00:29:14,579
[SPEAKER_00] Sin moje boli.

906
00:29:14,579 --> 00:29:16,599
[SPEAKER_00] Međutim, Jakov kaže ne,

907
00:29:16,599 --> 00:29:18,440
[SPEAKER_00] on ima jedan pozitivniji stav

908
00:29:18,440 --> 00:29:20,119
[SPEAKER_00] i on kaže zvače se Benjamin.

909
00:29:20,440 --> 00:29:23,160
[SPEAKER_00] A Benjamin znači sin moje desnice.

910
00:29:23,160 --> 00:29:25,720
[SPEAKER_00] Naravno, znate i sami,

911
00:29:25,720 --> 00:29:27,099
[SPEAKER_00] još od prošloga puta,

912
00:29:27,099 --> 00:29:28,259
[SPEAKER_00] da je muškarac taj,

913
00:29:28,259 --> 00:29:29,940
[SPEAKER_00] otac je taj koji daje zadnju riječ,

914
00:29:29,940 --> 00:29:32,599
[SPEAKER_00] dakle, kako će se sin zvati.

915
00:29:32,599 --> 00:29:33,140
[SPEAKER_00] Jel tako?

916
00:29:33,140 --> 00:29:34,900
[SPEAKER_00] I u slučaju Isusa,

917
00:29:34,900 --> 00:29:36,160
[SPEAKER_00] i u slučaju Ivana Krstitelja,

918
00:29:36,160 --> 00:29:37,400
[SPEAKER_00] sjetite se kada smo zadnji puta

919
00:29:37,400 --> 00:29:38,480
[SPEAKER_00] pričali o tome.

920
00:29:38,480 --> 00:29:41,839
[SPEAKER_00] Dakle, tko je sin boli?

921
00:29:41,839 --> 00:29:44,279
[SPEAKER_00] Dakle, znamo ko je prvorođenac Marijin.

922
00:29:44,279 --> 00:29:45,299
[SPEAKER_00] Nove Rahele.

923
00:29:45,299 --> 00:29:48,220
[SPEAKER_00] To je, dakle, Rahel je to Josip Egipatski,

924
00:29:48,220 --> 00:29:49,619
[SPEAKER_00] Isus je Mariji.

925
00:29:50,299 --> 00:29:52,380
[SPEAKER_00] Onaj koji je drugi sin,

926
00:29:52,380 --> 00:29:54,279
[SPEAKER_00] Raheli, je Benjamin.

927
00:29:54,279 --> 00:29:56,559
[SPEAKER_00] Tko je Marijin drugi sin?

928
00:29:56,559 --> 00:29:57,759
[SPEAKER_00] Ivan.

929
00:29:57,759 --> 00:30:00,240
[SPEAKER_00] Sjetite se, sin boli.

930
00:30:00,240 --> 00:30:00,980
[SPEAKER_00] Ben, oni.

931
00:30:01,480 --> 00:30:02,579
[SPEAKER_00] Situacije pod križem.

932
00:30:02,579 --> 00:30:05,039
[SPEAKER_00] Ivan 19.25.

933
00:30:05,039 --> 00:30:07,839
[SPEAKER_00] Uz križ su Isus ostajale majka njegova,

934
00:30:07,839 --> 00:30:09,420
[SPEAKER_00] zatim sestra njegove majke,

935
00:30:09,420 --> 00:30:11,240
[SPEAKER_00] Marija Kleofina i Marija Magdalena.

936
00:30:11,240 --> 00:30:13,900
[SPEAKER_00] Kad Isus vidje majku i krajnje učenika

937
00:30:13,900 --> 00:30:14,799
[SPEAKER_00] koje ga je ljubio,

938
00:30:14,799 --> 00:30:17,079
[SPEAKER_00] reče majci, ženo, evo ti sina.

939
00:30:17,079 --> 00:30:20,180
[SPEAKER_00] Zatim reče učeniku, evo ti majke.

940
00:30:20,259 --> 00:30:22,460
[SPEAKER_00] I od toga časa uze je učenik sebe.

941
00:30:22,460 --> 00:30:25,500
[SPEAKER_00] Vidite, i ovdje jednu snažnu paralelu sa Rahelom.

942
00:30:25,500 --> 00:30:29,559
[SPEAKER_00] Vi znate, dakle, u ovom događaju križa,

943
00:30:29,559 --> 00:30:31,380
[SPEAKER_00] mi vjerujemo, rađa se crkva.

944
00:30:31,380 --> 00:30:34,099
[SPEAKER_00] Dakle, u događaju križa rađa se crkva.

945
00:30:34,599 --> 00:30:39,019
[SPEAKER_00] I to rađanje, zaista, za razliku kada Marija rađa Isusa Krista,

946
00:30:39,019 --> 00:30:42,160
[SPEAKER_00] muči da je bezgrešna, dakle, nema porođajnih boli.

947
00:30:42,160 --> 00:30:45,099
[SPEAKER_00] Mi znamo da su porođajne boli, još od knjige Postanka,

948
00:30:45,099 --> 00:30:47,900
[SPEAKER_00] dakle, posljedica istočnog grijeha.

949
00:30:47,900 --> 00:30:50,119
[SPEAKER_00] Budi će da Marija je oslobođena istočnog grijeha,

950
00:30:50,119 --> 00:30:52,220
[SPEAKER_00] ona kada u Betlehemu rađa Krista,

951
00:30:52,220 --> 00:30:54,000
[SPEAKER_00] ona ne osjeća porođajne boli.

952
00:30:54,000 --> 00:30:58,920
[SPEAKER_00] Te porođajne boli su odgođene do događaja križa.

953
00:30:58,920 --> 00:31:01,880
[SPEAKER_00] Tamo Marija, ajmo reći, u duhovnom smislu,

954
00:31:02,640 --> 00:31:04,819
[SPEAKER_00] duhovne porođajne boli, ne fizičke,

955
00:31:04,819 --> 00:31:08,059
[SPEAKER_00] nego duhovne porođajne boli, rađa crkvu.

956
00:31:08,059 --> 00:31:10,640
[SPEAKER_00] Rađa, ajmo reći, drugoga sina,

957
00:31:10,640 --> 00:31:13,880
[SPEAKER_00] dakle, koje ga uzima k sebi, Ben Oni, sin boli,

958
00:31:13,880 --> 00:31:15,700
[SPEAKER_00] Marija je ovdje kao Rahela,

959
00:31:15,700 --> 00:31:18,519
[SPEAKER_00] majka boli, ona koja pati, koja trpi,

960
00:31:18,519 --> 00:31:22,680
[SPEAKER_00] dakle, i preko toga uzima svakoga od nas.

961
00:31:22,680 --> 00:31:25,400
[SPEAKER_00] Vidite, tu jednu duboku biblijsku mistiku ovdje,

962
00:31:25,400 --> 00:31:27,319
[SPEAKER_00] u ovoj baš snažnoj paraleli.

963
00:31:27,319 --> 00:31:29,279
[SPEAKER_00] Dakle, tako sam i ovdje stavio,

964
00:31:29,279 --> 00:31:30,799
[SPEAKER_00] može treća tablica, molim te.

965
00:31:32,400 --> 00:31:34,700
[SPEAKER_00] Dakle, roditelji Izrela i roditelji crkve,

966
00:31:34,700 --> 00:31:36,880
[SPEAKER_00] roditelji Izrela su Jakov i Rahela,

967
00:31:36,880 --> 00:31:39,460
[SPEAKER_00] dakle, Josip je prvorođeni od Rahela,

968
00:31:39,460 --> 00:31:40,900
[SPEAKER_00] Isus je prvorođeni od Marije,

969
00:31:40,900 --> 00:31:43,619
[SPEAKER_00] Benjamin je sin Raheline boli,

970
00:31:43,619 --> 00:31:46,500
[SPEAKER_00] Ivan je sin Marijine boli,

971
00:31:46,500 --> 00:31:47,539
[SPEAKER_00] je li tako, pod križe,

972
00:31:47,539 --> 00:31:50,140
[SPEAKER_00] i, dakle, taj naziv ljubljeni,

973
00:31:50,140 --> 00:31:51,700
[SPEAKER_00] zašto Ivan za sebe kaže,

974
00:31:51,700 --> 00:31:53,920
[SPEAKER_00] ja sam ljubljeni, jer skvaća

975
00:31:53,920 --> 00:31:55,619
[SPEAKER_00] svoju paralelu sa Benjaminom.

976
00:31:55,619 --> 00:31:58,140
[SPEAKER_00] Dakle, odite kako, skvaća svoju paralelu sa Benjaminom.

977
00:31:59,220 --> 00:32:01,859
[SPEAKER_00] Dakle, 12 sinova, Benjamin je ljubljeni.

978
00:32:01,859 --> 00:32:04,180
[SPEAKER_00] U ponovljenom zakonu, ima taj naziv ljubljeni,

979
00:32:04,180 --> 00:32:06,099
[SPEAKER_00] u ponovljenom zakonu, 33.12,

980
00:32:06,099 --> 00:32:07,140
[SPEAKER_00] o Benjaminu reče,

981
00:32:07,140 --> 00:32:09,140
[SPEAKER_00] gospodinu je on ljubljeni,

982
00:32:09,140 --> 00:32:09,619
[SPEAKER_00] grčki,

983
00:32:09,619 --> 00:32:11,440
[SPEAKER_00] ega pemenos,

984
00:32:11,440 --> 00:32:13,200
[SPEAKER_00] i u miru svak da počiva.

985
00:32:13,200 --> 00:32:14,819
[SPEAKER_00] Višni ga šiti svih njegovih dana,

986
00:32:14,819 --> 00:32:16,599
[SPEAKER_00] između njegovih prebjeva bregova.

987
00:32:16,940 --> 00:32:19,680
[SPEAKER_00] Tako i kod 12-storice apostola,

988
00:32:19,680 --> 00:32:20,579
[SPEAKER_00] Ivan je ljubljeni,

989
00:32:20,579 --> 00:32:22,299
[SPEAKER_00] ima isti naziv kao i Benjamin,

990
00:32:22,299 --> 00:32:24,039
[SPEAKER_00] a to je ega pemenos.

991
00:32:24,039 --> 00:32:26,740
[SPEAKER_00] Dakle, eto, zato on sebe naziva,

992
00:32:26,740 --> 00:32:28,099
[SPEAKER_00] ja sam taj ljubljeni učenik.

993
00:32:28,099 --> 00:32:29,000
[SPEAKER_00] Ne u smislu ono,

994
00:32:29,000 --> 00:32:31,059
[SPEAKER_00] nikog drugog Isusa ne voli nego samo mene,

995
00:32:31,059 --> 00:32:33,299
[SPEAKER_00] nego zato što on je svjestan,

996
00:32:33,299 --> 00:32:34,940
[SPEAKER_00] svoje, dakle,

997
00:32:34,940 --> 00:32:37,579
[SPEAKER_00] da je njega Benjamin nagovjestio.

998
00:32:37,579 --> 00:32:38,119
[SPEAKER_00] Razumijete?

999
00:32:38,220 --> 00:32:39,380
[SPEAKER_00] Kao što i svakoga,

1000
00:32:39,380 --> 00:32:41,980
[SPEAKER_00] svako 12-storice braće,

1001
00:32:41,980 --> 00:32:44,759
[SPEAKER_00] bilo bi zanimljivo da praviti jednu katehezu

1002
00:32:44,759 --> 00:32:48,019
[SPEAKER_00] da je pravilo paralelu sa 12-storicom apostola.

1003
00:32:48,019 --> 00:32:48,539
[SPEAKER_00] Ok.

1004
00:32:48,539 --> 00:32:52,259
[SPEAKER_00] E sada, pokolj nevide dječice.

1005
00:32:52,259 --> 00:32:54,299
[SPEAKER_00] Gdje je tu uloga svete obitelji?

1006
00:32:54,299 --> 00:32:55,319
[SPEAKER_00] Oni samo bježe,

1007
00:32:55,319 --> 00:32:57,099
[SPEAKER_00] spašavaju živu glavu

1008
00:32:57,099 --> 00:32:58,680
[SPEAKER_00] i boli i priga za neviju dječicu.

1009
00:32:58,680 --> 00:32:59,839
[SPEAKER_00] Jelimo vidjeti sad.

1010
00:32:59,839 --> 00:33:01,500
[SPEAKER_00] U nevidoj dječici mi znamo,

1011
00:33:01,500 --> 00:33:04,900
[SPEAKER_00] zapravo vidimo prve mučenike crkve,

1012
00:33:04,900 --> 00:33:08,099
[SPEAKER_00] u smislu oni prvi koji su dali svoje,

1013
00:33:08,220 --> 00:33:11,160
[SPEAKER_00] svoje živote zbog Isusa Hrista.

1014
00:33:11,160 --> 00:33:12,980
[SPEAKER_00] Pogledajte sada ovo.

1015
00:33:12,980 --> 00:33:15,420
[SPEAKER_00] Dakle, Matej 2.16-21.

1016
00:33:15,420 --> 00:33:17,859
[SPEAKER_00] Vidješi da su ga mudraci izigrali,

1017
00:33:17,859 --> 00:33:19,240
[SPEAKER_00] Herod se silno rasrdi

1018
00:33:19,240 --> 00:33:21,680
[SPEAKER_00] i poslao poubijati sve dječake u Betlehemu

1019
00:33:21,680 --> 00:33:22,779
[SPEAKER_00] i po svojoj okolici

1020
00:33:22,779 --> 00:33:24,319
[SPEAKER_00] o dvije godine na niže,

1021
00:33:24,319 --> 00:33:26,619
[SPEAKER_00] prema vremenu što ga razazna od mudraca.

1022
00:33:26,619 --> 00:33:28,039
[SPEAKER_00] Tada se ispuni,

1023
00:33:28,039 --> 00:33:29,599
[SPEAKER_00] dakle, tu je tek ispunjenje,

1024
00:33:29,599 --> 00:33:32,380
[SPEAKER_00] tada se ispuni što je rečeno po proroku Jeremiji.

1025
00:33:32,380 --> 00:33:33,700
[SPEAKER_00] U rabi se čuje,

1026
00:33:33,700 --> 00:33:35,960
[SPEAKER_00] i sa glas čuje, kuknjava i plać gorak.

1027
00:33:36,380 --> 00:33:38,559
[SPEAKER_00] Rahela oplakuje sinove svoje.

1028
00:33:38,559 --> 00:33:40,339
[SPEAKER_00] Tko je ovdje Rahela?

1029
00:33:40,339 --> 00:33:41,519
[SPEAKER_00] Marija.

1030
00:33:41,519 --> 00:33:44,380
[SPEAKER_00] Marija nije samo ona koja bježi,

1031
00:33:44,380 --> 00:33:45,740
[SPEAKER_00] nego oplakuje.

1032
00:33:45,740 --> 00:33:47,920
[SPEAKER_00] Čitav događaj dok bježi.

1033
00:33:47,920 --> 00:33:49,559
[SPEAKER_00] I neće da se utješi,

1034
00:33:49,559 --> 00:33:51,299
[SPEAKER_00] jer više ih nema.

1035
00:33:51,299 --> 00:33:53,180
[SPEAKER_00] Nakon Herodova skončanja,

1036
00:33:53,180 --> 00:33:55,779
[SPEAKER_00] gle, ađao se gospodin javi u snu Josipu u Egiptu,

1037
00:33:55,779 --> 00:33:58,279
[SPEAKER_00] ustani reči uzmi djete i njegov majku,

1038
00:33:58,279 --> 00:33:59,599
[SPEAKER_00] te pođu u zemlju Izraelsku,

1039
00:33:59,599 --> 00:34:02,660
[SPEAKER_00] jer su umrli oni koji su djetetu u glavi radili.

1040
00:34:03,359 --> 00:34:05,339
[SPEAKER_00] Dakle, vi ovdje imate situaciju,

1041
00:34:05,339 --> 00:34:10,599
[SPEAKER_00] Dakle, Jakov odgovara, rekli smo svetome Josipu.

1042
00:34:10,599 --> 00:34:12,960
[SPEAKER_00] Tko je Jakovljev stariji brat?

1043
00:34:12,960 --> 00:34:16,579
[SPEAKER_00] Ezav, je li tako? Ezav.

1044
00:34:16,579 --> 00:34:19,820
[SPEAKER_00] Jesi se sjećate na prvom susetu o svetome Josipu?

1045
00:34:19,820 --> 00:34:23,039
[SPEAKER_00] Dakle, tko je Ezav ove linije?

1046
00:34:23,039 --> 00:34:24,440
[SPEAKER_00] Koji kralj?

1047
00:34:24,820 --> 00:34:25,619
[SPEAKER_00] Herod.

1048
00:34:25,619 --> 00:34:27,739
[SPEAKER_00] Dakle, i ovdje vidite kako sve nekako,

1049
00:34:27,739 --> 00:34:29,980
[SPEAKER_00] koji je onak super fantastični roman,

1050
00:34:29,980 --> 00:34:32,199
[SPEAKER_00] koji onak ima jako dobrog pripovjedača,

1051
00:34:32,199 --> 00:34:34,219
[SPEAKER_00] koji je ono što je posijao na početku,

1052
00:34:34,219 --> 00:34:35,900
[SPEAKER_00] nekako se na kraju žalje, jel?

1053
00:34:35,900 --> 00:34:38,659
[SPEAKER_00] Ono, raspet koji ima smisla je jako povezan

1054
00:34:38,659 --> 00:34:41,159
[SPEAKER_00] sa svime onome što se sijalo u priče na početku.

1055
00:34:41,159 --> 00:34:45,099
[SPEAKER_00] Dakle, ovdje imate sukom između Josipa i Heroda,

1056
00:34:45,099 --> 00:34:46,719
[SPEAKER_00] kao što ste imali sukom,

1057
00:34:46,719 --> 00:34:48,559
[SPEAKER_00] dakle, u ovom slučaju ne vede dječice,

1058
00:34:48,559 --> 00:34:51,900
[SPEAKER_00] kao što ste imali sukom između Jakova i Ezava.

1059
00:34:52,400 --> 00:34:53,900
[SPEAKER_00] Dakle, vidite ovdje.

1060
00:34:53,900 --> 00:34:58,320
[SPEAKER_00] E sada, što vidimo u ovom izvještaju

1061
00:34:58,320 --> 00:34:59,599
[SPEAKER_00] o pokolju ne vede dječice?

1062
00:34:59,599 --> 00:35:03,239
[SPEAKER_00] Prvo pokolj se događa u blizini Raheline grobnice,

1063
00:35:03,239 --> 00:35:04,139
[SPEAKER_00] dakle, u Betlehemu.

1064
00:35:04,139 --> 00:35:05,260
[SPEAKER_00] Mi znamo da je Rahela,

1065
00:35:05,260 --> 00:35:07,739
[SPEAKER_00] za razliku od Rebeke,

1066
00:35:07,739 --> 00:35:08,679
[SPEAKER_00] za razliku od care,

1067
00:35:08,679 --> 00:35:11,239
[SPEAKER_00] nije pokopana u obiteljskoj grobnici,

1068
00:35:11,239 --> 00:35:13,239
[SPEAKER_00] nego baš prema Betlehemu.

1069
00:35:13,239 --> 00:35:16,519
[SPEAKER_00] Isto proročki, isto providonosno.

1070
00:35:16,519 --> 00:35:18,719
[SPEAKER_00] Baš kao što je Rahela pokopana,

1071
00:35:18,719 --> 00:35:20,519
[SPEAKER_00] dakle, na putu prema Betlehemu.

1072
00:35:20,639 --> 00:35:22,420
[SPEAKER_00] Tako su i nevina dječica.

1073
00:35:22,420 --> 00:35:23,900
[SPEAKER_00] Oni su morali biti tamo pokopani.

1074
00:35:23,900 --> 00:35:26,480
[SPEAKER_00] Rahela oplakuje izabrani narod

1075
00:35:26,480 --> 00:35:27,679
[SPEAKER_00] u babilonskom progonstvu,

1076
00:35:27,679 --> 00:35:30,059
[SPEAKER_00] Marija oplakuje novi izabrani narod

1077
00:35:30,059 --> 00:35:32,400
[SPEAKER_00] u ovom progonstvu,

1078
00:35:32,400 --> 00:35:33,239
[SPEAKER_00] kralja Heroda,

1079
00:35:33,239 --> 00:35:34,800
[SPEAKER_00] i kasnije u rimskom progonstvu.

1080
00:35:34,800 --> 00:35:36,000
[SPEAKER_00] Dakle, mučenici,

1081
00:35:36,000 --> 00:35:39,179
[SPEAKER_00] za one koji umiru zbog njenoga sina.

1082
00:35:39,179 --> 00:35:41,260
[SPEAKER_00] Dakle, Rahela i Marija,

1083
00:35:41,260 --> 00:35:41,960
[SPEAKER_00] ovo je važno,

1084
00:35:41,960 --> 00:35:45,019
[SPEAKER_00] nisu samo simbolika patničke majke.

1085
00:35:45,019 --> 00:35:47,300
[SPEAKER_00] Ono, ja idem nekom simbolu patnje.

1086
00:35:47,420 --> 00:35:50,280
[SPEAKER_00] One su stvarne osobe koje su pruživjale svoju patnju

1087
00:35:50,280 --> 00:35:51,260
[SPEAKER_00] i koje, dakle,

1088
00:35:51,260 --> 00:35:55,139
[SPEAKER_00] ne samo zbog vlastite patnje pate,

1089
00:35:55,139 --> 00:35:55,639
[SPEAKER_00] jel,

1090
00:35:55,639 --> 00:35:56,579
[SPEAKER_00] dakle,

1091
00:35:56,579 --> 00:35:59,340
[SPEAKER_00] Rahela dok je rađala Benjamina

1092
00:35:59,340 --> 00:36:01,000
[SPEAKER_00] i Marija dok je bila pod križem,

1093
00:36:01,000 --> 00:36:03,559
[SPEAKER_00] nego one se poisto vječuju

1094
00:36:03,559 --> 00:36:06,260
[SPEAKER_00] i sa svim patnjama svoga naroda.

1095
00:36:06,260 --> 00:36:07,539
[SPEAKER_00] Dakle, kao što je ovdje

1096
00:36:07,539 --> 00:36:08,179
[SPEAKER_00] Remy napisao

1097
00:36:08,179 --> 00:36:09,559
[SPEAKER_00] Rahela oplakuje sinove

1098
00:36:09,559 --> 00:36:11,239
[SPEAKER_00] koji su sada u babelovskom služajstvu,

1099
00:36:11,239 --> 00:36:13,320
[SPEAKER_00] Rahela već odavno nema,

1100
00:36:13,320 --> 00:36:15,420
[SPEAKER_00] tako i ovdje Marija i dan danas

1101
00:36:15,420 --> 00:36:17,900
[SPEAKER_00] dakle su osjeća i pati sa nama

1102
00:36:17,900 --> 00:36:19,539
[SPEAKER_00] koji isto patimo

1103
00:36:19,539 --> 00:36:21,239
[SPEAKER_00] zbog imena Isusa Hrista.

1104
00:36:21,239 --> 00:36:22,099
[SPEAKER_00] Dakle, evo,

1105
00:36:22,099 --> 00:36:23,800
[SPEAKER_00] zato je važna ova paralela.

1106
00:36:23,800 --> 00:36:24,960
[SPEAKER_00] Međutim,

1107
00:36:24,960 --> 00:36:27,300
[SPEAKER_00] idemo vidjeti gdje tu Josipova patnja za crku.

1108
00:36:27,300 --> 00:36:29,300
[SPEAKER_00] Vidjeli smo Marijinu patnju za crku.

1109
00:36:29,300 --> 00:36:31,199
[SPEAKER_00] Gdje tu Josipova patnja za crku.

1110
00:36:31,840 --> 00:36:32,719
[SPEAKER_00] Pogledajte sada ovo.

1111
00:36:32,719 --> 00:36:35,139
[SPEAKER_00] Jel se sjećate onog najpoznatijeg

1112
00:36:35,139 --> 00:36:37,000
[SPEAKER_00] sna Josipa Egipatskog?

1113
00:36:37,000 --> 00:36:37,780
[SPEAKER_00] Saznate?

1114
00:36:37,780 --> 00:36:39,599
[SPEAKER_00] Ono, baš san zbog kojega su ga

1115
00:36:39,599 --> 00:36:41,159
[SPEAKER_00] zamrzila njegova braća.

1116
00:36:41,159 --> 00:36:41,940
[SPEAKER_00] Pročitaću ga.

1117
00:36:41,940 --> 00:36:44,360
[SPEAKER_00] Postanak 37.9.11.

1118
00:36:44,360 --> 00:36:47,579
[SPEAKER_00] Usni on još jedan san

1119
00:36:47,579 --> 00:36:49,039
[SPEAKER_00] te ga ispriča svoje braće.

1120
00:36:49,039 --> 00:36:49,659
[SPEAKER_00] Ovdje ćemo vidjeti

1121
00:36:49,659 --> 00:36:51,420
[SPEAKER_00] da se sveti Josip spominje

1122
00:36:51,420 --> 00:36:52,360
[SPEAKER_00] i u knjizi otkrivenja.

1123
00:36:52,360 --> 00:36:53,820
[SPEAKER_00] A, sad je to tumači,

1124
00:36:53,820 --> 00:36:55,179
[SPEAKER_00] ali kada nije u knjizi otkrivenja.

1125
00:36:55,179 --> 00:36:55,820
[SPEAKER_00] Dobro, ok.

1126
00:36:55,820 --> 00:36:58,820
[SPEAKER_00] Dakle, postanak 37.9.11.

1127
00:36:58,820 --> 00:37:01,360
[SPEAKER_00] Dakle, Josip Egipatski.

1128
00:37:01,440 --> 00:37:02,880
[SPEAKER_00] Usni on još jedan san

1129
00:37:02,880 --> 00:37:04,500
[SPEAKER_00] te ga ispriča svoje braći.

1130
00:37:04,500 --> 00:37:06,639
[SPEAKER_00] Još sam jedan san usnuo.

1131
00:37:06,639 --> 00:37:08,440
[SPEAKER_00] Pazite, sunce, mjesec

1132
00:37:08,440 --> 00:37:09,500
[SPEAKER_00] i jedana iz zvijezda

1133
00:37:09,500 --> 00:37:10,800
[SPEAKER_00] duboko mi se klanjahu.

1134
00:37:10,800 --> 00:37:12,960
[SPEAKER_00] Kad je to ispričao svome otcu,

1135
00:37:12,960 --> 00:37:14,480
[SPEAKER_00] ukori ga otac i reče mu

1136
00:37:14,480 --> 00:37:16,579
[SPEAKER_00] što znači taj san što si ga usnuo?

1137
00:37:16,579 --> 00:37:17,639
[SPEAKER_00] Zar ćemo doći ja,

1138
00:37:17,639 --> 00:37:19,119
[SPEAKER_00] tvoja majka i tvoja braća

1139
00:37:19,119 --> 00:37:22,139
[SPEAKER_00] pa ti se do zemlje klanjati?

1140
00:37:22,139 --> 00:37:23,760
[SPEAKER_00] Dok su braća od zavisti

1141
00:37:23,760 --> 00:37:24,920
[SPEAKER_00] bila ljuta na nj,

1142
00:37:24,920 --> 00:37:27,559
[SPEAKER_00] njegov je otac razmišljao o svemu.

1143
00:37:27,559 --> 00:37:29,960
[SPEAKER_00] Zapamtite san.

1144
00:37:29,960 --> 00:37:31,039
[SPEAKER_00] Dakle, Josipu

1145
00:37:31,039 --> 00:37:32,000
[SPEAKER_00] Josipu se klanjaju

1146
00:37:32,000 --> 00:37:34,460
[SPEAKER_00] sunce, mjesec i jedana iz zvijezda.

1147
00:37:34,460 --> 00:37:36,320
[SPEAKER_00] Dakle, i vidimo odmah

1148
00:37:36,320 --> 00:37:37,300
[SPEAKER_00] tumačenje toga sna.

1149
00:37:37,300 --> 00:37:39,079
[SPEAKER_00] Jedana iz zvijezda su njegova braća,

1150
00:37:39,079 --> 00:37:41,119
[SPEAKER_00] sunce je otac,

1151
00:37:41,119 --> 00:37:42,980
[SPEAKER_00] mjesec je majka.

1152
00:37:42,980 --> 00:37:44,739
[SPEAKER_00] Dakle, simbolika toga sna.

1153
00:37:46,199 --> 00:37:48,360
[SPEAKER_00] Otkrivenje 12.1.4 kaže ovo.

1154
00:37:48,360 --> 00:37:50,880
[SPEAKER_00] I znamenje veliko pokaza se na nebu.

1155
00:37:51,300 --> 00:37:52,920
[SPEAKER_00] žena odjeve na suncem,

1156
00:37:52,920 --> 00:37:54,320
[SPEAKER_00] mjesec je pod nogama,

1157
00:37:54,320 --> 00:37:56,639
[SPEAKER_00] a na glavi vijenac od 12 zvijezda.

1158
00:37:56,980 --> 00:37:59,679
[SPEAKER_00] trudna viče u porođajnim bolima i mukama rađanja.

1159
00:37:59,679 --> 00:38:01,860
[SPEAKER_00] I pokaza se drugo znamenje na nebu.

1160
00:38:01,860 --> 00:38:02,139
[SPEAKER_00] Gle,

1161
00:38:02,139 --> 00:38:03,099
[SPEAKER_00] zmaj velik,

1162
00:38:03,099 --> 00:38:05,059
[SPEAKER_00] ognjen sa sedam glava i deset rogova,

1163
00:38:05,059 --> 00:38:06,760
[SPEAKER_00] na glava mu sedam kruna,

1164
00:38:06,760 --> 00:38:09,219
[SPEAKER_00] a repu povlači trećinu zvijezda nebeskih

1165
00:38:09,219 --> 00:38:10,380
[SPEAKER_00] i obori ih na zemlju.

1166
00:38:10,380 --> 00:38:11,960
[SPEAKER_00] Zmaj strade pred ženu,

1167
00:38:11,960 --> 00:38:12,940
[SPEAKER_00] koja imaše roditi,

1168
00:38:12,940 --> 00:38:13,880
[SPEAKER_00] da joj čim rodi,

1169
00:38:13,880 --> 00:38:14,599
[SPEAKER_00] prožre djete.

1170
00:38:14,599 --> 00:38:16,260
[SPEAKER_00] Dakle, ovdje imamo ženu

1171
00:38:16,260 --> 00:38:19,320
[SPEAKER_00] koja rađa u porođajnim bolima.

1172
00:38:19,719 --> 00:38:21,760
[SPEAKER_00] Dakle, ta žena je crkva.

1173
00:38:21,760 --> 00:38:22,639
[SPEAKER_00] Mi znamo,

1174
00:38:22,639 --> 00:38:25,440
[SPEAKER_00] dakle, ima vrlo slične opise sa Marijom,

1175
00:38:25,440 --> 00:38:27,059
[SPEAKER_00] jer Marija je prototip crkve.

1176
00:38:27,059 --> 00:38:28,000
[SPEAKER_00] Međutim,

1177
00:38:28,000 --> 00:38:30,119
[SPEAKER_00] i zato što se ovo čita na Veliku Gospu,

1178
00:38:30,119 --> 00:38:31,280
[SPEAKER_00] to je uglavnom prvo čitanje,

1179
00:38:31,280 --> 00:38:34,699
[SPEAKER_00] međutim, ovdje prije svega riječ o crkvi.

1180
00:38:34,699 --> 00:38:36,199
[SPEAKER_00] I pogledajte sada ovo.

1181
00:38:36,199 --> 00:38:38,719
[SPEAKER_00] Dakle, žena ovako,

1182
00:38:38,719 --> 00:38:40,480
[SPEAKER_00] mjesticio je pod nogama.

1183
00:38:40,480 --> 00:38:41,980
[SPEAKER_00] Dakle, simbol Rahele.

1184
00:38:41,980 --> 00:38:42,719
[SPEAKER_00] Sjetite se,

1185
00:38:42,719 --> 00:38:43,699
[SPEAKER_00] iz Josipovog sna.

1186
00:38:43,699 --> 00:38:46,340
[SPEAKER_00] Dakle, ona je ta koja je nad Izraelom,

1187
00:38:46,340 --> 00:38:47,679
[SPEAKER_00] koja sada vlada Izraelom.

1188
00:38:47,679 --> 00:38:49,079
[SPEAKER_00] Rahela je majka Izrela.

1189
00:38:49,719 --> 00:38:53,360
[SPEAKER_00] Za ogrluta je odjevena je suncem.

1190
00:38:53,360 --> 00:38:55,039
[SPEAKER_00] Od tuda je ona simbolika,

1191
00:38:55,039 --> 00:38:55,840
[SPEAKER_00] prije svega,

1192
00:38:55,840 --> 00:38:59,900
[SPEAKER_00] dakle, što Josip u egipatskom ljubljenom je sinu,

1193
00:38:59,900 --> 00:39:01,320
[SPEAKER_00] Jakov poklanja?

1194
00:39:01,320 --> 00:39:05,320
[SPEAKER_00] Kako?

1195
00:39:05,320 --> 00:39:06,699
[SPEAKER_00] Ogrtač.

1196
00:39:06,699 --> 00:39:08,099
[SPEAKER_00] Dakle, ogrtač koji je šaren,

1197
00:39:08,099 --> 00:39:11,159
[SPEAKER_00] koji je, dakle, u bojama.

1198
00:39:11,159 --> 00:39:14,079
[SPEAKER_00] Možda je otišao Hugo Boss pa mu je uzelo neku košuljicu.

1199
00:39:14,079 --> 00:39:15,860
[SPEAKER_00] Vjerotno, tada bi to napravio.

1200
00:39:15,860 --> 00:39:17,699
[SPEAKER_00] Sve najbolje za sina.

1201
00:39:17,699 --> 00:39:20,960
[SPEAKER_00] Ovaj, ali tada je samo imao neki šaren jogrtač.

1202
00:39:20,960 --> 00:39:22,219
[SPEAKER_00] Dobro, ok.

1203
00:39:22,219 --> 00:39:24,199
[SPEAKER_00] Dakle, ta simbolika,

1204
00:39:24,199 --> 00:39:26,019
[SPEAKER_00] da je otac taj koji,

1205
00:39:26,019 --> 00:39:28,099
[SPEAKER_00] dakle, biblijski,

1206
00:39:28,099 --> 00:39:29,760
[SPEAKER_00] to je biblijska gesta.

1207
00:39:29,760 --> 00:39:31,559
[SPEAKER_00] Otac je taj koji odjeva,

1208
00:39:31,559 --> 00:39:33,900
[SPEAKER_00] odnosno, otac je taj koji zaodjeva,

1209
00:39:33,900 --> 00:39:35,679
[SPEAKER_00] koji zaogrnjuje, možemo reći.

1210
00:39:35,679 --> 00:39:37,800
[SPEAKER_00] Dakle, ovdje je žena odjevena suncem.

1211
00:39:37,800 --> 00:39:39,519
[SPEAKER_00] Ona, možemo reći, crkva,

1212
00:39:39,519 --> 00:39:41,380
[SPEAKER_00] je zaogrnuta svetim Josipom.

1213
00:39:41,440 --> 00:39:42,380
[SPEAKER_00] Dakle, jer je ovdje,

1214
00:39:42,380 --> 00:39:44,440
[SPEAKER_00] dakle, Josipom, novim ocem,

1215
00:39:44,440 --> 00:39:45,579
[SPEAKER_00] stari otac je Jakov,

1216
00:39:45,579 --> 00:39:46,519
[SPEAKER_00] novi otac je Josip.

1217
00:39:46,519 --> 00:39:50,400
[SPEAKER_00] Dakle, to je ta snažna simbolika.

1218
00:39:50,400 --> 00:39:52,340
[SPEAKER_00] Jakov je zaogrnuo Josipa,

1219
00:39:52,340 --> 00:39:55,219
[SPEAKER_00] ovdje imamo, dakle, žena je odjevena,

1220
00:39:55,219 --> 00:39:57,420
[SPEAKER_00] odnosno, zaogrnuta suncem.

1221
00:39:57,420 --> 00:40:00,619
[SPEAKER_00] E sada, što to zapravo konkretno znači?

1222
00:40:02,320 --> 00:40:05,659
[SPEAKER_00] Ovako, to znači da je pod zaštitom svetoga Josipa,

1223
00:40:05,659 --> 00:40:06,840
[SPEAKER_00] ali tako, vrlo jednostavno.

1224
00:40:06,840 --> 00:40:09,619
[SPEAKER_00] Ok, pralik je Josipov grtač s mnogo boja.

1225
00:40:09,619 --> 00:40:12,179
[SPEAKER_00] E ovako, zbog svojih patnja i kušnji,

1226
00:40:12,179 --> 00:40:13,940
[SPEAKER_00] sve ono što je jako prošao,

1227
00:40:13,940 --> 00:40:16,159
[SPEAKER_00] sjetite se jako, imamo jedan patnički put,

1228
00:40:16,159 --> 00:40:17,780
[SPEAKER_00] Josip isto tako,

1229
00:40:17,780 --> 00:40:21,920
[SPEAKER_00] oni su zaslužili biti očevi i zaštitnici naroda.

1230
00:40:21,920 --> 00:40:23,980
[SPEAKER_00] Dakle, bilo Izrela, bilo crkve.

1231
00:40:23,980 --> 00:40:25,920
[SPEAKER_00] Pogledajte sada, svi ću završiti,

1232
00:40:25,920 --> 00:40:29,360
[SPEAKER_00] koje su to, koje su to, ovaj, paralele.

1233
00:40:29,360 --> 00:40:30,260
[SPEAKER_00] Dakle, vidite ovdje,

1234
00:40:31,019 --> 00:40:35,440
[SPEAKER_00] žena od Jevoda suncem.

1235
00:40:35,440 --> 00:40:36,940
[SPEAKER_00] Josip je, dakle, s Marijom,

1236
00:40:36,940 --> 00:40:40,619
[SPEAKER_00] a tako i s crkvom koja je u boli,

1237
00:40:40,619 --> 00:40:41,300
[SPEAKER_00] u njenoj boli.

1238
00:40:41,300 --> 00:40:44,599
[SPEAKER_00] Dakle, crkva je prikazana kao žena u boli,

1239
00:40:44,599 --> 00:40:45,679
[SPEAKER_00] u porođenim bolima.

1240
00:40:45,679 --> 00:40:47,719
[SPEAKER_00] Dakle, kao što je s Marijom Josip,

1241
00:40:47,719 --> 00:40:49,480
[SPEAKER_00] tako je i sa crkvom,

1242
00:40:49,480 --> 00:40:50,920
[SPEAKER_00] dok je u bolima.

1243
00:40:50,920 --> 00:40:53,579
[SPEAKER_00] Ovdje je to prikazao simbolom porođenim boli.

1244
00:40:53,579 --> 00:40:55,659
[SPEAKER_00] Dakle, crkva je zaogrluta,

1245
00:40:55,659 --> 00:40:56,900
[SPEAKER_00] ajmo reći, s svetim Josipom.

1246
00:40:56,900 --> 00:40:59,119
[SPEAKER_00] To je ono što Biblija ovdje zapravo želi

1247
00:40:59,119 --> 00:41:02,420
[SPEAKER_00] prikazati upravo ovim istim izričajima i simbolima.

1248
00:41:02,420 --> 00:41:05,500
[SPEAKER_00] Što zapravo možemo izvući na temelju

1249
00:41:05,500 --> 00:41:07,460
[SPEAKER_00] paralele Jakova i Josipa?

1250
00:41:07,460 --> 00:41:09,219
[SPEAKER_00] Što otac čini?

1251
00:41:09,219 --> 00:41:11,340
[SPEAKER_00] Otac za crku, sveti Josip,

1252
00:41:11,340 --> 00:41:13,559
[SPEAKER_00] ali ono što možemo reći na tragu

1253
00:41:13,559 --> 00:41:14,880
[SPEAKER_00] onoga što ćemo najsnažnije,

1254
00:41:14,880 --> 00:41:17,000
[SPEAKER_00] najviše raditi sljedećeg puta,

1255
00:41:17,119 --> 00:41:22,239
[SPEAKER_00] što otac kao takav čini onda i za svoj narod,

1256
00:41:22,239 --> 00:41:23,699
[SPEAKER_00] za svoju obitelj.

1257
00:41:23,699 --> 00:41:24,840
[SPEAKER_00] Prije svega,

1258
00:41:24,840 --> 00:41:28,039
[SPEAKER_00] bori se za blagoslov za svoje obitelj.

1259
00:41:28,039 --> 00:41:29,780
[SPEAKER_00] Bori se za blagoslov svoje obitelji.

1260
00:41:29,780 --> 00:41:31,900
[SPEAKER_00] Sjedite se, dakle, Jakov,

1261
00:41:31,900 --> 00:41:34,840
[SPEAKER_00] koji je prvo na prijaviru želio dobiti blagoslov,

1262
00:41:34,840 --> 00:41:38,739
[SPEAKER_00] a drugo, bilo mu je važno da autentično dobije blagoslov,

1263
00:41:39,099 --> 00:41:40,840
[SPEAKER_00] kada se ide vratiti Ezavu,

1264
00:41:40,840 --> 00:41:43,739
[SPEAKER_00] kada se ide, dakle, vratiti svojme ocu Izaku,

1265
00:41:43,739 --> 00:41:45,239
[SPEAKER_00] kada se on bori,

1266
00:41:45,239 --> 00:41:47,420
[SPEAKER_00] dakle, u one noći prije nego što je

1267
00:41:47,420 --> 00:41:49,059
[SPEAKER_00] kod Penuel, jel,

1268
00:41:49,059 --> 00:41:51,699
[SPEAKER_00] prijeći, kada se bori sa samim Bogom,

1269
00:41:51,699 --> 00:41:52,280
[SPEAKER_00] za blagoslov.

1270
00:41:52,280 --> 00:41:53,860
[SPEAKER_00] Neću te pustiti dok me ne blagosloviu.

1271
00:41:53,860 --> 00:41:54,800
[SPEAKER_00] Sjedite se citata.

1272
00:41:54,800 --> 00:41:56,059
[SPEAKER_00] Dakle, to je prva stvar.

1273
00:41:56,059 --> 00:41:58,719
[SPEAKER_00] Dakle, on se bori za blagoslov svoje obitelji.

1274
00:41:58,719 --> 00:42:01,280
[SPEAKER_00] Gdje vidimo da se Josip bori za blagoslov svoje,

1275
00:42:01,280 --> 00:42:02,800
[SPEAKER_00] sve te obitelji?

1276
00:42:02,800 --> 00:42:04,960
[SPEAKER_00] Time što dostup ide u Jeruzalem.

1277
00:42:04,960 --> 00:42:05,659
[SPEAKER_00] Vi se sjetite,

1278
00:42:06,260 --> 00:42:08,739
[SPEAKER_00] zadnji puta sam rekao da u Jeruzalem

1279
00:42:08,739 --> 00:42:11,340
[SPEAKER_00] nisu išli niti žene, niti djeca.

1280
00:42:11,340 --> 00:42:14,019
[SPEAKER_00] Josip ide zajedno i sa Marijom,

1281
00:42:14,019 --> 00:42:15,639
[SPEAKER_00] uvijek, kaže se, po običaju.

1282
00:42:15,639 --> 00:42:17,780
[SPEAKER_00] Dakle, i sa Marijom, i sa Isusom,

1283
00:42:17,780 --> 00:42:18,860
[SPEAKER_00] koji je tada još bio djete,

1284
00:42:18,860 --> 00:42:20,719
[SPEAKER_00] ide u Jeruzalem, a nije trebao.

1285
00:42:20,719 --> 00:42:22,860
[SPEAKER_00] Dakle, tu se vidi Josipova borba

1286
00:42:22,860 --> 00:42:25,199
[SPEAKER_00] za blagoslov svoje obitelji.

1287
00:42:25,199 --> 00:42:28,360
[SPEAKER_00] Drugo, iskupljuje grijehe i sramotu.

1288
00:42:28,360 --> 00:42:29,239
[SPEAKER_00] To je ono što otac.

1289
00:42:29,239 --> 00:42:31,780
[SPEAKER_00] Iskupljuje grijehe i sramotu svoje obitelji,

1290
00:42:31,780 --> 00:42:33,179
[SPEAKER_00] svoje loze, kako god želite.

1291
00:42:33,179 --> 00:42:34,820
[SPEAKER_00] Dakle, vidimo u Josipu,

1292
00:42:34,920 --> 00:42:37,179
[SPEAKER_00] koji je nije htio izvrnuti Mariju sramoti.

1293
00:42:37,179 --> 00:42:39,360
[SPEAKER_00] Sjetite se situacije Jakova,

1294
00:42:39,360 --> 00:42:43,219
[SPEAKER_00] dakle, le, pa onda onih služavki,

1295
00:42:43,219 --> 00:42:44,960
[SPEAKER_00] kogubina i tako dalje.

1296
00:42:44,960 --> 00:42:47,699
[SPEAKER_00] I htio je naravno vratiti isto čast

1297
00:42:47,699 --> 00:42:49,800
[SPEAKER_00] svojoj, ajmo reći, izakove obitelji,

1298
00:42:49,800 --> 00:42:51,000
[SPEAKER_00] jer on bi odbjegli sin,

1299
00:42:51,000 --> 00:42:53,099
[SPEAKER_00] zbog lažnog, ajmo reći,

1300
00:42:53,099 --> 00:42:54,940
[SPEAKER_00] lažno stečenog blagoslova,

1301
00:42:54,940 --> 00:42:56,360
[SPEAKER_00] ukraljenog blagoslova.

1302
00:42:56,360 --> 00:42:59,039
[SPEAKER_00] Dakle, iskupljuje grijehe i sramotu,

1303
00:42:59,039 --> 00:43:00,019
[SPEAKER_00] sramotu svoje obitelji.

1304
00:43:00,019 --> 00:43:02,179
[SPEAKER_00] Treće, štiti u progonstvu

1305
00:43:02,179 --> 00:43:03,659
[SPEAKER_00] i tješi u mučaništu.

1306
00:43:03,739 --> 00:43:05,900
[SPEAKER_00] Dakle, vidimo, s obzirom na situaciju

1307
00:43:05,900 --> 00:43:08,019
[SPEAKER_00] nevede dječice, s obzirom na bjeg u Egipat,

1308
00:43:08,019 --> 00:43:10,559
[SPEAKER_00] kod Jakova, vidimo kako on

1309
00:43:10,559 --> 00:43:13,300
[SPEAKER_00] u toj gladi ide sa svojim narodom

1310
00:43:13,300 --> 00:43:15,300
[SPEAKER_00] u Egipat, po žito, po pšenicu.

1311
00:43:15,300 --> 00:43:17,539
[SPEAKER_00] Isto tako i tamo ostaje u Egiptu.

1312
00:43:17,539 --> 00:43:19,659
[SPEAKER_00] Onda, riskira život

1313
00:43:19,659 --> 00:43:21,219
[SPEAKER_00] za sigurnost i zaštitu.

1314
00:43:21,219 --> 00:43:22,860
[SPEAKER_00] Dakle, to je ono, dakle,

1315
00:43:22,860 --> 00:43:24,980
[SPEAKER_00] četvrta stvar koju otac čini,

1316
00:43:24,980 --> 00:43:26,880
[SPEAKER_00] što prepoznamo isto i kod Jakova,

1317
00:43:26,880 --> 00:43:28,679
[SPEAKER_00] isto i kod svetoga Josipa.

1318
00:43:29,400 --> 00:43:31,260
[SPEAKER_00] i ono onako duholomistično,

1319
00:43:31,260 --> 00:43:35,340
[SPEAKER_00] a to je da svaku bol pretvara u pobjedu.

1320
00:43:35,340 --> 00:43:39,059
[SPEAKER_00] Dakle, i to vidimo u tome što je Jakov intervenirao

1321
00:43:39,059 --> 00:43:40,840
[SPEAKER_00] na ime Ben-Oni.

1322
00:43:40,840 --> 00:43:45,219
[SPEAKER_00] Dakle, Ben-Oni je pretvorio u Bin-Jamin.

1323
00:43:45,219 --> 00:43:48,539
[SPEAKER_00] Dakle, Ben-Oni, sin boli, je pretvorio u sina pobjede.

1324
00:43:48,679 --> 00:43:50,539
[SPEAKER_00] U smislu, Ben-Jamin sam rekao,

1325
00:43:50,539 --> 00:43:52,500
[SPEAKER_00] znači, sin moje desnice.

1326
00:43:52,500 --> 00:43:54,099
[SPEAKER_00] I to je zapravo,

1327
00:43:54,099 --> 00:43:56,619
[SPEAKER_00] tu se najviše, ovom zadnjem petom,

1328
00:43:56,619 --> 00:43:58,119
[SPEAKER_00] se najviše zapravo očituje

1329
00:43:58,119 --> 00:44:00,119
[SPEAKER_00] slika nebeskog očestva.

1330
00:44:00,119 --> 00:44:01,760
[SPEAKER_00] To je nešto što nebeski otac čini.

1331
00:44:01,760 --> 00:44:04,519
[SPEAKER_00] Dakle, otac uzima svoga sina boli,

1332
00:44:04,519 --> 00:44:05,440
[SPEAKER_00] Isusa Hrista,

1333
00:44:05,440 --> 00:44:08,260
[SPEAKER_00] i uzvisuje ga sebi z desna.

1334
00:44:08,260 --> 00:44:09,820
[SPEAKER_00] Dakle, evo, to je ono,

1335
00:44:09,820 --> 00:44:11,000
[SPEAKER_00] bol pretvara u pobjedu.

1336
00:44:11,000 --> 00:44:12,619
[SPEAKER_00] To sam onako, tako nekako,

1337
00:44:12,619 --> 00:44:15,139
[SPEAKER_00] nekako, ovaj, nazvao.

1338
00:44:15,139 --> 00:44:15,559
[SPEAKER_00] Ok.

1339
00:44:16,900 --> 00:44:18,139
[SPEAKER_00] Evo, jedna onako,

1340
00:44:18,139 --> 00:44:21,380
[SPEAKER_00] skroz, skroz biblijska perspektiva,

1341
00:44:21,380 --> 00:44:22,519
[SPEAKER_00] biblijska paralela,

1342
00:44:22,519 --> 00:44:23,539
[SPEAKER_00] da vidite zapravo,

1343
00:44:23,539 --> 00:44:26,420
[SPEAKER_00] kao što se za Isusa kaže,

1344
00:44:26,420 --> 00:44:28,239
[SPEAKER_00] da je novi Adam,

1345
00:44:28,239 --> 00:44:29,760
[SPEAKER_00] novi Mojsije,

1346
00:44:29,760 --> 00:44:32,099
[SPEAKER_00] zašto je Isus novi Adam?

1347
00:44:32,099 --> 00:44:33,880
[SPEAKER_00] U smislu savršenog čovjeka.

1348
00:44:33,880 --> 00:44:35,539
[SPEAKER_00] Novi Mojsije u smislu

1349
00:44:35,539 --> 00:44:38,119
[SPEAKER_00] novog savršenog izbavitelja.

1350
00:44:38,119 --> 00:44:39,940
[SPEAKER_00] Da je novi David u smislu

1351
00:44:39,940 --> 00:44:40,940
[SPEAKER_00] savršenog kralja.

1352
00:44:40,940 --> 00:44:43,619
[SPEAKER_00] I vidjeli smo da je novi Josip Egipatski

1353
00:44:43,619 --> 00:44:45,079
[SPEAKER_00] u smislu savršenog patnika,

1354
00:44:45,079 --> 00:44:46,880
[SPEAKER_00] jer Josip Egipatski je baš patnička.

1355
00:44:46,900 --> 00:44:48,340
[SPEAKER_00] lik u starom je zavjetu.

1356
00:44:48,340 --> 00:44:50,019
[SPEAKER_00] Tako, kao što smo vidjeli,

1357
00:44:50,019 --> 00:44:51,519
[SPEAKER_00] Marija je nova Rahela,

1358
00:44:51,519 --> 00:44:52,320
[SPEAKER_00] nova Eva,

1359
00:44:52,320 --> 00:44:53,239
[SPEAKER_00] nova Rebeka,

1360
00:44:53,239 --> 00:44:53,920
[SPEAKER_00] nova Ruta,

1361
00:44:53,920 --> 00:44:54,480
[SPEAKER_00] ako želite.

1362
00:44:54,480 --> 00:44:55,719
[SPEAKER_00] O tome isto možemo pričati.

1363
00:44:55,719 --> 00:44:58,440
[SPEAKER_00] Tako je i Josip Novi Jakov.

1364
00:44:58,440 --> 00:45:00,019
[SPEAKER_00] On je novozavjetni patrijarh,

1365
00:45:00,019 --> 00:45:01,780
[SPEAKER_00] novozavjetni pravotac naše vjere,

1366
00:45:01,780 --> 00:45:03,019
[SPEAKER_00] prvi kršćanin.

1367
00:45:03,019 --> 00:45:04,519
[SPEAKER_00] Kao što je Marija prva kršćanka,

1368
00:45:04,519 --> 00:45:06,699
[SPEAKER_00] Sveti Josip je prvi kršćanin

1369
00:45:06,699 --> 00:45:08,320
[SPEAKER_00] i vidimo na koji način

1370
00:45:08,320 --> 00:45:10,340
[SPEAKER_00] njegovo očinstvo

1371
00:45:10,340 --> 00:45:11,980
[SPEAKER_00] zakrinjuje, dakle,

1372
00:45:11,980 --> 00:45:13,900
[SPEAKER_00] crkvu, ženu koja je odjevena

1373
00:45:13,900 --> 00:45:15,380
[SPEAKER_00] zaugrnuta suncem,

1374
00:45:15,380 --> 00:45:15,920
[SPEAKER_00] a vidjeli smo

1375
00:45:15,920 --> 00:45:17,679
[SPEAKER_00] mjesec znači majka

1376
00:45:17,679 --> 00:45:18,579
[SPEAKER_00] u Bibliji,

1377
00:45:18,579 --> 00:45:19,539
[SPEAKER_00] a sunce znači

1378
00:45:19,539 --> 00:45:20,579
[SPEAKER_00] znači otac.

1379
00:45:21,260 --> 00:45:23,219
[SPEAKER_00] Evo, ima li neko kakvo pitanje?

1380
00:45:23,219 --> 00:45:27,079
[SPEAKER_00] Što?

1381
00:45:27,079 --> 00:45:28,320
[SPEAKER_00] Da, izvolite.

1382
00:45:28,320 --> 00:45:34,940
[SPEAKER_00] Da, nemojte vam sad pitati

1383
00:45:34,940 --> 00:45:37,440
[SPEAKER_00] s kim, jer moram...

1384
00:45:37,440 --> 00:45:45,159
[SPEAKER_00] Da, dobro,

1385
00:45:45,159 --> 00:45:46,460
[SPEAKER_00] juda, u smislu.

1386
00:45:46,460 --> 00:45:48,559
[SPEAKER_00] Gledaju se jedan istorica.

1387
00:45:48,559 --> 00:45:50,659
[SPEAKER_00] Dakle, jedan istorica

1388
00:45:50,659 --> 00:45:52,739
[SPEAKER_00] koja poslije pedesetnice

1389
00:45:52,739 --> 00:45:54,320
[SPEAKER_00] jude tada nema

1390
00:45:54,320 --> 00:45:55,539
[SPEAKER_00] dok nije došao Matej, jel?

1391
00:45:55,539 --> 00:45:56,940
[SPEAKER_00] Tako da, da.

1392
00:45:56,940 --> 00:46:00,079
[SPEAKER_00] Ali mi jedan pot možemo to napraviti

1393
00:46:00,079 --> 00:46:00,519
[SPEAKER_00] da vidite.

1394
00:46:00,519 --> 00:46:01,199
[SPEAKER_00] Evo, čisto.

1395
00:46:01,199 --> 00:46:03,440
[SPEAKER_00] Da nije neka na tegnutom priča.

1396
00:46:03,440 --> 00:46:04,159
[SPEAKER_00] Dalje.

1397
00:46:04,159 --> 00:46:07,599
[SPEAKER_00] Izvolite.

1398
00:46:07,599 --> 00:46:13,079
[SPEAKER_00] Rahela.

1399
00:46:13,079 --> 00:46:13,820
[SPEAKER_00] Ne, ne.

1400
00:46:13,820 --> 00:46:14,539
[SPEAKER_00] Ono je zapravo,

1401
00:46:14,539 --> 00:46:15,260
[SPEAKER_00] ajmo reći,

1402
00:46:15,260 --> 00:46:18,000
[SPEAKER_00] značenje Rahele za židove

1403
00:46:18,000 --> 00:46:19,199
[SPEAKER_00] isto značenje

1404
00:46:19,199 --> 00:46:20,820
[SPEAKER_00] kako Marija ima za nas.

1405
00:46:20,820 --> 00:46:21,539
[SPEAKER_00] Dakle,

1406
00:46:21,539 --> 00:46:25,199
[SPEAKER_00] znaju se gdje je grob.

1407
00:46:25,199 --> 00:46:26,940
[SPEAKER_00] Recimo, zanimljivo je,

1408
00:46:26,940 --> 00:46:28,780
[SPEAKER_00] Efrata je mjesto

1409
00:46:28,780 --> 00:46:29,940
[SPEAKER_00] gdje je Rahela pokopana.

1410
00:46:29,940 --> 00:46:31,019
[SPEAKER_00] Kako se zove mjesto

1411
00:46:31,019 --> 00:46:32,039
[SPEAKER_00] gdje je Marija umrla

1412
00:46:32,039 --> 00:46:33,960
[SPEAKER_00] i gdje je uznesena na nebo?

1413
00:46:35,079 --> 00:46:35,539
[SPEAKER_00] Efez.

1414
00:46:35,539 --> 00:46:37,719
[SPEAKER_00] Dakle, Efez, tu sam si zapisao.

1415
00:46:37,719 --> 00:46:39,920
[SPEAKER_00] Efrata i Efez imaju isto značenje.

1416
00:46:39,920 --> 00:46:41,519
[SPEAKER_00] Savo malo.

1417
00:46:41,519 --> 00:46:43,820
[SPEAKER_00] Ispričan, tu sam si baš zapisao ono za svake stvari.

1418
00:46:43,820 --> 00:46:44,000
[SPEAKER_00] Da.

1419
00:46:44,000 --> 00:46:46,739
[SPEAKER_00] Dakle, Efrata i Efezus,

1420
00:46:46,739 --> 00:46:48,340
[SPEAKER_00] na grečkom Efrata je o hebriski,

1421
00:46:48,340 --> 00:46:49,539
[SPEAKER_00] znači poželjan.

1422
00:46:49,539 --> 00:46:51,719
[SPEAKER_00] Poželjan, to znači kao,

1423
00:46:51,719 --> 00:46:52,840
[SPEAKER_00] znači je ti gradova.

1424
00:46:52,840 --> 00:46:54,840
[SPEAKER_00] Ali hoću reći da imaju različite imena,

1425
00:46:54,840 --> 00:46:57,300
[SPEAKER_00] zapravo čak možda onako onomatopejski i slična,

1426
00:46:57,800 --> 00:46:59,360
[SPEAKER_00] ali imaju isto značenje, jel?

1427
00:46:59,360 --> 00:47:01,940
[SPEAKER_00] Dakle, vidimo i tu zapravo isto paralelu,

1428
00:47:01,940 --> 00:47:04,579
[SPEAKER_00] po mjestima gdje su preminule,

1429
00:47:04,579 --> 00:47:06,880
[SPEAKER_00] odnosno Marija je usnula u jednom i u drugom.

1430
00:47:06,880 --> 00:47:07,960
[SPEAKER_00] Dakle, hoću reći,

1431
00:47:07,960 --> 00:47:10,960
[SPEAKER_00] Rahela se smatra jednom velikom zagovornicom

1432
00:47:10,960 --> 00:47:11,920
[SPEAKER_00] židovskog naroda.

1433
00:47:11,920 --> 00:47:14,139
[SPEAKER_00] Dakle, to je ono što Jeremija isto kaže.

1434
00:47:14,139 --> 00:47:15,719
[SPEAKER_00] Rahela oplakuje svoje sinove,

1435
00:47:15,719 --> 00:47:17,420
[SPEAKER_00] Rahela više, ajmo reći, nema.

1436
00:47:17,420 --> 00:47:18,719
[SPEAKER_00] Znači, ima tu svijest.

1437
00:47:18,719 --> 00:47:20,739
[SPEAKER_00] Rahela je dalje sa svojim narodom.

1438
00:47:20,739 --> 00:47:22,619
[SPEAKER_00] Ona je majka Izrela,

1439
00:47:22,619 --> 00:47:25,460
[SPEAKER_00] majka dvanestorice, možemo reći,

1440
00:47:25,559 --> 00:47:27,119
[SPEAKER_00] ako ne u biološkom smislu, jel?

1441
00:47:27,119 --> 00:47:30,360
[SPEAKER_00] Jer ovo su joj, ajmo reći, posljenci,

1442
00:47:30,360 --> 00:47:33,679
[SPEAKER_00] odnosno nečaci zapravo neki način,

1443
00:47:33,679 --> 00:47:34,940
[SPEAKER_00] Lea je bila sestra, da?

1444
00:47:34,940 --> 00:47:37,500
[SPEAKER_00] To je sve tako zbrtljeno u tom starom zavijetu.

1445
00:47:37,500 --> 00:47:40,260
[SPEAKER_00] Ali uglavnom, evo, da se vrati na pitanje,

1446
00:47:40,260 --> 00:47:42,280
[SPEAKER_00] Rahela je baš prototip Marije.

1447
00:47:42,280 --> 00:47:44,059
[SPEAKER_00] Evo, ima isti status u židovskom,

1448
00:47:44,059 --> 00:47:45,159
[SPEAKER_00] starom i zabranom narodu,

1449
00:47:45,159 --> 00:47:46,579
[SPEAKER_00] kao što Marija ima kod nas.

1450
00:47:46,579 --> 00:47:48,320
[SPEAKER_00] Izvolite.

1451
00:47:48,320 --> 00:47:50,699
[SPEAKER_00] Kako bi žena u otkrivene,

1452
00:47:50,699 --> 00:47:53,159
[UNKNOWN] znači žena koja je zavljena s moncem,

1453
00:47:53,159 --> 00:47:54,659
[UNKNOWN] može predstaviti crkvu,

1454
00:47:54,659 --> 00:47:56,500
[UNKNOWN] ako ona rađa Isusa,

1455
00:47:56,500 --> 00:47:58,800
[UNKNOWN] a crkve je Isusine zavijenice?

1456
00:47:58,800 --> 00:48:01,300
[SPEAKER_00] Ovako, dakle,

1457
00:48:01,300 --> 00:48:03,380
[SPEAKER_00] prije svega,

1458
00:48:03,380 --> 00:48:05,860
[SPEAKER_00] crkva rađa Isusa

1459
00:48:05,860 --> 00:48:07,199
[SPEAKER_00] na Euharistiji.

1460
00:48:07,199 --> 00:48:09,860
[SPEAKER_00] Dakle, bez crkve nema Euharistije,

1461
00:48:09,860 --> 00:48:12,460
[SPEAKER_00] kao što li nema crkve bez Euharistije.

1462
00:48:12,460 --> 00:48:14,039
[SPEAKER_00] Dakle, u tom smislu.

1463
00:48:15,619 --> 00:48:19,380
[SPEAKER_00] Iako ovo tumačenje,

1464
00:48:19,380 --> 00:48:20,840
[SPEAKER_00] ovo nije rađanje Krista,

1465
00:48:20,840 --> 00:48:22,800
[SPEAKER_00] porodi sina i tako dalje.

1466
00:48:22,800 --> 00:48:26,119
[SPEAKER_00] Zato, to je rađanje, dakle, potomstva.

1467
00:48:26,119 --> 00:48:27,460
[SPEAKER_00] Mi smo Marijini potomci.

1468
00:48:27,460 --> 00:48:28,679
[SPEAKER_00] Vi vidite zapravo,

1469
00:48:28,679 --> 00:48:31,239
[SPEAKER_00] zmaj je taj koji čeka da prožirje djete.

1470
00:48:31,239 --> 00:48:33,159
[SPEAKER_00] Dakle, to je progostvo crkve.

1471
00:48:33,159 --> 00:48:36,900
[SPEAKER_00] Odnosno, progostvo djece crkve.

1472
00:48:36,900 --> 00:48:39,019
[SPEAKER_00] Dakle, kada smo radili knjigu Otkrivenja,

1473
00:48:39,019 --> 00:48:40,019
[SPEAKER_00] sjetite se,

1474
00:48:40,019 --> 00:48:41,340
[SPEAKER_00] dakle, to sam baš tumačio,

1475
00:48:41,340 --> 00:48:42,239
[SPEAKER_00] to je,

1476
00:48:42,840 --> 00:48:46,079
[SPEAKER_00] zmaj je uvijek tu prisutan,

1477
00:48:46,079 --> 00:48:47,159
[SPEAKER_00] da nas prožirje.

1478
00:48:47,159 --> 00:48:49,739
[SPEAKER_00] U smislu napasti, kušnji, progostva i tako dalje.

1479
00:48:49,739 --> 00:48:53,019
[SPEAKER_00] Dakle, ovo je aluzija kao da je riječ o Mariji,

1480
00:48:53,019 --> 00:48:54,320
[SPEAKER_00] ali zapravo,

1481
00:48:54,320 --> 00:48:57,320
[SPEAKER_00] dakle, mi smo svi Kristova braća i sestre,

1482
00:48:57,320 --> 00:48:58,860
[SPEAKER_00] zato ide to rađanje nas.

1483
00:48:59,179 --> 00:49:00,940
[SPEAKER_00] I to je crkva koja rađa nas.

1484
00:49:00,940 --> 00:49:07,000
[SPEAKER_00] Dakle, to u tom simbolu potomka koji je muškića,

1485
00:49:07,000 --> 00:49:08,380
[SPEAKER_00] kako se ovdje opisuje i tako dalje.

1486
00:49:08,380 --> 00:49:11,579
[SPEAKER_00] Dakle, ovdje nije opisano Marijino rađanje Krista,

1487
00:49:11,579 --> 00:49:13,219
[SPEAKER_00] jer to je bezbolno rađanje,

1488
00:49:13,219 --> 00:49:16,619
[SPEAKER_00] nego, ajmo reći, crkvino rađanje nas.

1489
00:49:16,619 --> 00:49:19,079
[SPEAKER_00] Dalje.

1490
00:49:19,079 --> 00:49:32,760
[SPEAKER_00] I zato ona bježi u pustinju.

1491
00:49:32,760 --> 00:49:35,119
[SPEAKER_00] Dakle, to je, ja sam opet na ovome.

1492
00:49:35,119 --> 00:49:36,420
[SPEAKER_00] Dakle, ona, sjedite se,

1493
00:49:36,420 --> 00:49:37,920
[SPEAKER_00] dakle, ona pobježe u pustinju,

1494
00:49:37,920 --> 00:49:40,639
[SPEAKER_00] dakle, nakon ovoga skriva se od zmaja,

1495
00:49:40,639 --> 00:49:41,699
[SPEAKER_00] bježi u pustinju,

1496
00:49:41,699 --> 00:49:43,659
[SPEAKER_00] jer je opet slika crkva je hodočasnička.

1497
00:49:43,659 --> 00:49:46,260
[SPEAKER_00] Dakle, kao što izraelski narod bio stariji

1498
00:49:46,260 --> 00:49:48,159
[SPEAKER_00] i izabrali narod, 14 godina u pustinji,

1499
00:49:48,619 --> 00:49:51,420
[SPEAKER_00] i crkva je ovdje u svojoj vrstnom izlasku.

1500
00:49:51,420 --> 00:49:53,079
[SPEAKER_00] Prema obječajnoj zemlji to je nebo, jel?

1501
00:49:53,079 --> 00:49:55,699
[SPEAKER_00] Zato je ta ista paralela, ista simbolika.

1502
00:49:55,699 --> 00:49:58,039
[SPEAKER_00] Dakle, crkva se pobježe u pustinju.

1503
00:49:58,039 --> 00:49:59,420
[SPEAKER_00] Mi se sada nalazimo,

1504
00:49:59,420 --> 00:50:01,840
[SPEAKER_00] mi smo hodočasnička crkva u pustinju, jel?

1505
00:50:01,840 --> 00:50:02,619
[SPEAKER_00] U ovome svijetu.

1506
00:50:02,619 --> 00:50:04,460
[SPEAKER_00] Dalje.

1507
00:50:04,460 --> 00:50:10,980
[SPEAKER_00] Ne mojte Bibliju doslovno čitati.

1508
00:50:10,980 --> 00:50:14,400
[SPEAKER_00] U smislu, pogotovo ne knjigu otkrivenja,

1509
00:50:14,400 --> 00:50:17,079
[SPEAKER_00] neću se opet vraćati na knjigu otkrivenja,

1510
00:50:17,079 --> 00:50:18,159
[SPEAKER_00] ali, evo,

1511
00:50:18,159 --> 00:50:20,500
[SPEAKER_00] najbolje vam je Bibliju

1512
00:50:20,500 --> 00:50:21,400
[SPEAKER_00] tumačiti Biblijom.

1513
00:50:21,400 --> 00:50:23,460
[SPEAKER_00] Tu ne možete fulat, evo.

1514
00:50:23,460 --> 00:50:28,300
[SPEAKER_00] Onda vam se neće dogoditi,

1515
00:50:28,300 --> 00:50:29,780
[SPEAKER_00] da ćete Josipa Egipatskog sporediti

1516
00:50:29,780 --> 00:50:30,519
[SPEAKER_00] sa svetim Josipom.

1517
00:50:34,119 --> 00:50:35,659
[SPEAKER_00] Dobro, možemo zaključiti, jel da?

1518
00:50:35,659 --> 00:50:37,039
[SPEAKER_00] Ok, čeka nas.

